olony
Governors<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-NZ style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-NZ'>T=
hese
characters can apply their bonuses to an entire colony. Assign them to a co=
lony
to see their effects.</span><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:E=
N-GB;
mso-no-proof:yes'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<h3><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-no-proof:yes'>S=
cientists<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-NZ style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-NZ'>T=
hese
characters can boost your Research output at a single Space Port or Research
