roop
Generals<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-NZ style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-NZ'>T=
hese
characters affect all troops on a planet or loaded onto a fleet. Assign the=
m to
a Fleet or a planet to see their effects.</span><span lang=3DEN-GB
